  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ゲームの開始時に、プレイヤーは古代中国における権力の初期配置を決定する6つのシナリオの中から1つを選びます。シナリオを選んだ後、プレイヤーは自分が操作する武将を決定します。各キャラクターには、戦闘、知力、政治、カリスマ、陸軍指揮、海軍指揮といったいくつかのステータスがあります。プレイヤーは中国の全ての領土を征服することでゲームに勝利します。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The player takes control of a master, a general capable of commanding as many states as he can acquire, and, if successful, unifies China. As many as eight may play, but only one can succeed. There are five chronologically arranged scenarios. The first has China in its most disorganized period and the last has virtually all of China controlled by one of three generals.\n\nThe precise requirements for success in each of these scenarios differs, but in all cases the goal is to rule as many states as possible. After the completion of any scenario but number five the game will automatically advance to the next. You may start the game at any scenario.\n\nThe third edition of this game with more game improvements.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
